commit.message:
(CPP_CPU_DEFAULT): Define if TARGET_CPU_DEFAULT is not set.

From-SVN: r13807

files.patch:
@@ -304,14 +304,14 @@ extern int ix86_arch;

 #define CPP_CPU_DEFAULT "-Di586"

 #endif /* TARGET_CPU_DEFAULT */
